title: Samurai (1986) issues #01 thru 05 Barry Blair -  Aircel
description:
this will be my last upload of SAMURAI until I finish all issues. I just finishing editing issue 5 so I thought I would post and get some feedback before I go any further. I tried not to overcompensate in photoshop but did try to remove all the artifacts. I just need someone to critique and make sure the issues are looking fine without too any glaring oversights.

I've scan the first 12 issues and i'm still on track to post all issues by the end of the august.

This one of the flagship titles from Aircel and the one I find surprisingly missing from the Aircel torrent floating around


Thanks

Enjoy
